(MAE Dashboard V3 - Technical and User Manual \(EN + IT\)) Tj
T*
(Version: 1.0) Tj
T*
(Project: mae-dashboard-v3) Tj
T*
(Date: 22 Mar 2026) Tj
T*
(Reference URL: https://www.maeservice.it/newui/) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1\) PROJECT OVERVIEW \(EN\)) Tj
T*
(MAE Dashboard V3 is a web dashboard used to monitor datalogger devices in near real time.) Tj
T*
(It provides device selection, KPIs, charts, table views, GPS map support, power monitoring,) Tj
T*
(alert thresholds, export tools, and API-driven integrations.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2\) PANORAMICA PROGETTO \(IT\)) Tj
T*
(MAE Dashboard V3 e una dashboard web per monitorare dispositivi datalogger quasi in tempo reale.) Tj
T*
(Fornisce selezione dispositivo, KPI, grafici, tabelle, supporto mappa GPS, monitoraggio) Tj
T*
(alimentazione, soglie allarmi, export e integrazioni API.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3\) TECHNOLOGY STACK \(EN\)) Tj
T*
(Programming languages:) Tj
T*
(- HTML5) Tj
T*
(- CSS3) Tj
T*
(- JavaScript ES6+) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Frameworks/libraries:) Tj
T*
(- No frontend framework \(no React/Vue/Angular\)) Tj
T*
(- No mandatory build framework) Tj
T*
(- Browser native APIs \(Fetch API, DOM, SVG\)) Tj
T*
(- Local dev server via live-server scripts) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Architecture:) Tj
T*
(- state.js: global state and initialization) Tj
T*
(- api.js: API layer and normalization) Tj
T*
(- render.js: UI rendering) Tj
T*
(- modals.js: modal workflows and interactions) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4\) STACK TECNOLOGICO \(IT\)) Tj
T*
(Linguaggi:) Tj
T*
(- HTML5) Tj
T*
(- CSS3) Tj
T*
(- JavaScript ES6+) Tj
