() Tj
T*
(Framework/librerie:) Tj
T*
(- Nessun framework frontend \(no React/Vue/Angular\)) Tj
T*
(- Nessun framework build obbligatorio) Tj
T*
(- API native browser \(Fetch API, DOM, SVG\)) Tj
T*
(- Server locale via script live-server) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Architettura:) Tj
T*
