(5\) CORE FUNCTIONALITY \(EN\)) Tj
T*
(- Device list and active device switching) Tj
T*
(- Device info \(battery, memory, GPS, network\)) Tj
T*
(- Measurement data loading with date filters) Tj
T*
(- Dynamic channel header handling) Tj
T*
(- KPI cards, main chart, mini charts, table log) Tj
T*
(- Alerts and thresholds panel) Tj
T*
(- Map modal with styles and quick navigation) Tj
T*
(- Power modal with Battery/USB/AUX trends) Tj
T*
(- Export in CSV, JSON, and browser print/PDF) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6\) FUNZIONALITA PRINCIPALI \(IT\)) Tj
T*
(- Lista dispositivi e cambio dispositivo attivo) Tj
T*
(- Device info \(batteria, memoria, GPS, rete\)) Tj
T*
(- Caricamento dati con filtri data) Tj
T*
(- Gestione dinamica header canali) Tj
T*
(- KPI, grafico principale, mini grafici, tabella misure) Tj
T*
(- Pannello allarmi e soglie) Tj
T*
(- Modale mappa con stili e navigazione rapida) Tj
T*
(- Modale alimentazione con trend Battery/USB/AUX) Tj
T*
(- Export CSV, JSON e stampa/PDF browser) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7\) NEW APIs INCLUDED \(EN\)) Tj
T*
(- File list endpoint:) Tj
T*
(  /api/v1/devices/:id/files/from/:from/to/:to/type/:type/limit/:limit/offset/:offset) Tj
T*
(  Supports type filter: evt | cir | day and pagination metadata.) Tj
T*
(- File download endpoint:) Tj
T*
(  /api/v1/devices/:id/file/:name) Tj
T*
(  Supports base64 payload download.) Tj
T*
(- Event details endpoint:) Tj
T*
(  /api/v1/devices/:id/event/:evt_id) Tj
T*
(  Shows event JSON details.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(UI additions:) Tj
T*
(- New "Device Files & Events" modal in Export) Tj
T*
(- Filters \(from/to/type\), paginated file list, per-file download) Tj
T*
(- Event details input + one-click from evt rows) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Device Info additions:) Tj
T*
(- IP field = ip + port) Tj
T*
(- Public IP field = ip_public + port_public) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8\) NUOVE API INCLUSE \(IT\)) Tj
T*
(- Endpoint elenco file:) Tj
T*
(  /api/v1/devices/:id/files/from/:from/to/:to/type/:type/limit/:limit/offset/:offset) Tj
T*
(  Supporta filtro tipo evt | cir | day e metadati paginazione.) Tj
T*
(- Endpoint download file:) Tj
T*
(  /api/v1/devices/:id/file/:name) Tj
T*
(  Supporta download da payload base64.) Tj
T*
(- Endpoint dettaglio evento:) Tj
T*
(  /api/v1/devices/:id/event/:evt_id) Tj
T*
(  Mostra dettagli JSON evento.) Tj
ET
